title: Bracquemont
description: An ancient place, cited: BAtlas 11 B3 Bracquemont

properties.description: A Celtic and a Gallo-Roman oppidum (52 ha) with a temple (fanum). The site is located at Camp de César (also Cité de Limes), commune Bracquemont / Neuville-lès-Dieppe, département Seine-Maritime.
properties.title: Center point of the site
